{"tid":961487,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"Epic Games靠《要塞英雄》2018年賺了30億美元","createTime":"2018-12-30T07:06:51.000Z","updateTime":"2018-12-30T12:18:49.000Z","uid":117200,"like":8,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":18,"replies":[{"pid":"041bc2f998636d31c127cf8e1bb6b9e4ef2fe594","tid":961487,"uid":117200,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-30T07:06:51.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"http://img.technews.tw/wp-content/uploads/2018/09/27144935/40565063420_42ab53ea50_b-624x351.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fimg.technews.tw%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2018%2F09%2F27144935%2F40565063420_42ab53ea50_b-624x351.jpg&h=fe494ad9&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n《要塞英雄》遊戲持續火紅，也讓遊戲開發商 Epic Games 賺飽飽。近日 TechCrunch 援引消息人士報導，整個 2018 年，Epic Games 已實現約 30 億美元盈利。<br />\n<br />\n雖然目前 Epic Games 尚未回應，但結果並不讓人意外。從 2018 年 3 月開始，《要塞英雄》每月營收就飛速上漲，之後更多次打破免費遊戲的盈利紀錄。<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.technews.tw/wp-content/uploads/2018/12/28150030/Console-in-game-revenue-SUPERDATA-1024x822-e1545980438247.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.technews.tw%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2018%2F12%2F28150030%2FConsole-in-game-revenue-SUPERDATA-1024x822-e1545980438247.png&h=b252e4b9&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n根據 SuperData 提供的數據，如果沒有《要塞英雄》的吸金大勢，同期主機遊戲行業的整體營收曲線甚至會從上升變成下降。<br />\n<br />\n優秀的營收表現，離不開 Epic Games 名為「戰鬥通行證」（Battle Pass）的激勵模式。具體來說，這套通行證相當一個超級大禮包，當你到達一定等級，就會解鎖相應的服裝、道具和遊戲貨幣。<br />\n<br />\n當然，通行證本身也有免費和付費版，免費版拿到的獎勵自然沒有付費版多，但如果你玩到 30 多級才願意花 10 美元買付費版，照樣可以獲得之前 0~30 級錯過的所有付費獎勵。<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.technews.tw/wp-content/uploads/2018/12/28145938/Fortnite-Game-screenshot-e1545980387969.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.technews.tw%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2018%2F12%2F28145938%2FFortnite-Game-screenshot-e1545980387969.jpg&h=b982dd7a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n初看之下，這種類似會員機制的設定似乎並無特別之處，但《要塞英雄》這種「花錢買福利」的模式，卻有效刺激用戶的參與度，還實現了六至七成用戶的付費率，這比市面大多數只有一成左右付費率的「Free-to-play」遊戲要高得多。<br />\n<br />\n《要塞英雄》對業界的影響還不只於此。一方面，免費下載和積極的跨平台策略，讓《要塞英雄》短時間收穫大量玩家。遊戲用戶量在 2018 年 11 月底突破 2 億大關，實際活躍用戶數也有近 8,000 萬人，龐大的規模，也成為推動 Sony 開放 PS4 跨平台遊戲連機的契機之一。<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.technews.tw/wp-content/uploads/2018/12/13161037/some-epic-store-games-are-pushing-back-or-scrapping-steam-releases-1-e1544688657412.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.technews.tw%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2018%2F12%2F13161037%2Fsome-epic-store-games-are-pushing-back-or-scrapping-steam-releases-1-e1544688657412.jpg&h=4c2d6e73&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n得益於《要塞英雄》的成功，Epic Games 也少不了資本方的青睞。2018 年 10 月完成新一輪融資後，目前 Epic Games 整體估值接近 150 億美元。這次的融資一共吸引到 7 家投資公司參與，這些新投資者包括 Smash Ventures、aXiomatic、Vulcan Capital、Kleiner Perkins、Lightspeed Venture、知名私募基金 KKR 以及矽谷資產管理公司 Iconiq Capital。<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.technews.tw/wp-content/uploads/2018/12/28145447/Epic-game-design-e1545980099920.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.technews.tw%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2018%2F12%2F28145447%2FEpic-game-design-e1545980099920.jpg&h=83972dee&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n在虛幻引擎（Unreal Engine）官網上公布的這項訊息中，Epic Games 表示，這些功能最初都是為《要塞英雄》（Fortnite）所建造，也隨著遊戲在 7 個平台與 2 億名玩家進行過戰鬥測試，2019 年起將陸續推出這一系列的遊戲服務功能，對所有引擎、所有平台和所有商店開放，同時對所有開發者來說都是免費的。<br />\n<br />\n<strong>核心功能（2019 年第 2-3 季）：跨平台登入、連線，將支援 7 個主要平台（PC、Mac、iOS、Android、PlayStation、Xbox、Switch）<br />\n跨平台組隊和配對（2019 年第 3-4 季至所有平台）<br />\n跨平台數據儲存、雲端遊戲（2019年第 2 季）</strong><br />\n<img src=\"https://img.technews.tw/wp-content/uploads/2018/09/27113435/6258fe2b00ba6b3f-624x351.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.technews.tw%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2018%2F09%2F27113435%2F6258fe2b00ba6b3f-624x351.jpg&h=aa4dd7ff&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n官網下載<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.epicgames.com/fortnite/en-US/buy-now/battle-royale\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.epicgames.com%2Ffortnite%2Fen-US%2Fbuy-now%2Fbattle-royale&d=64hfh1fhp%2Fb782P9UO5lbRFQyUQXuyYblCT5RSyYNoQ%3D&h=a990d534\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.epicgames.com/fortnite/en-US/buy-now/battle-royale</a>"},{"pid":"48bb30af1444bc7b94804cabfcf2be7ae3a00d2a","tid":961487,"uid":157510,"like":4,"dislike":14,"score":-10,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-12-30T07:10:38.000Z","msg":"我pubg轉過嚟既，前晚dl咗佢，玩到依家都仲未訓，真係好好玩<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"82cbd86088f32501c1f75a88abd31d590e661234","tid":961487,"uid":33848,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-12-30T07:11:28.000Z","msg":"唔少家長荷包受害"},{"pid":"64a686ea24be0b70691b30b4b73f6180bdf5602a","tid":961487,"uid":149494,"like":14,"dislike":3,"score":11,"quote":{"pid":"48bb30af1444bc7b94804cabfcf2be7ae3a00d2a","tid":961487,"uid":157510,"like":4,"dislike":14,"score":-10,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-12-30T07:10:38.000Z","msg":"我pubg轉過嚟既，前晚dl咗佢，玩到依家都仲未訓，真係好好玩<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-12-30T07:18:00.000Z","msg":"打手味濃到<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9f54be88af8d285ef9b4f51f2a5e12646e35ca9f","tid":961487,"uid":157510,"like":4,"dislike":1,"score":3,"quote":{"pid":"82cbd86088f32501c1f75a88abd31d590e661234","tid":961487,"uid":33848,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-12-30T07:11:28.000Z","msg":"唔少家長荷包受害"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-30T07:18:51.000Z","msg":"係，我偷咗媽咪張信用卡買點<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f8ee9e3b82c253e222f1c3ae452f52a0dcf46d4a","tid":961487,"uid":144,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"82cbd86088f32501c1f75a88abd31d590e661234","tid":961487,"uid":33848,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-12-30T07:11:28.000Z","msg":"唔少家長荷包受害"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-12-30T07:19:12.000Z","msg":"真係好多美國小學雞偷家長張信用卡課金<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img 