億！高於30幾個國家GDP</span></strong><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://exp.gg/wp-content/uploads/2018/12/fortnite-battle-royale-ninja-blevins-e1546077598101.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fexp.gg%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2018%2F12%2Ffortnite-battle-royale-ninja-blevins-e1546077598101.jpg&h=c3055b27&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n《要塞英雄》實況界的大紅人 Ninja 與遊戲可以說是互惠，在 Twitch 上多達 1,270 百萬追隨者，YouTube 上有 1,600 萬名訂閲者，每個月從《要塞英雄》直播中賺取 50 萬美元。早在 2009 年就開始電競生涯的他，在《最後一戰 3》、《H1Z1》以及《絕地求生》等遊戲中累積不少粉絲，並以此為基礎開始直播《要塞英雄》後，人氣翻倍成長。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://pbs.twimg.com/ext_tw_video_thumb/976616984052994048/pu/img/elAK5KmZ813Ps0G1?format=jpg&amp;name=small\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fpbs.twimg.com%2Fext_tw_video_thumb%2F976616984052994048%2Fpu%2Fimg%2FelAK5KmZ813Ps0G1%3Fformat%3Djpg%26name%3Dsmall&h=1065ba35&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n《要塞英雄》的魅力，球員也抵擋不了。NBA 紐約尼克隊的教練接受訪問時就曾表示，他目前最大的敵人就是《要塞英雄》，比波士頓塞爾提克隊還要更難對付，球員們甚至願意犧牲睡眠熬夜去打遊戲。去年 10 月 NBA 球星 Gordon Hayward 在賽場上扭斷腳踝，接受治療與養傷期間，讓他也成為了《要塞英雄》的忠實粉絲。除了 NBA 球星們，足球選手、棒球選手也熱愛《要塞英雄》並願意為其熬夜。"},{"pid":"60e6adfa9862d7f5cd46f917d928b4f65c67e948","tid":961487,"uid":24788,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"quote":{"pid":"b9e8620027104f03702e84c2ed32f1a3e71f27be","tid":961487,"uid":51933,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"d3b4794375a981d3268522c11ebd23035ed6d280","tid":961487,"uid":59518,"like":3,"dislike":1,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"b63795ffc0a52f88cca9fcf93ed69eaff1c2142c","tid":961487,"uid":24788,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-12-30T07:21:53.000Z","msg":"Qq仲唔收購佢"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-12-30T07:31:42.000Z","msg":"巴打坐左好多年<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n騰訊在<span style=\"color: red;\">2012年7月</span>以3.3億美元收購EpicGames已發行股本48.4%的股份。財報指出，EpicGames已屬騰訊集團的聯營公司，且騰訊有權在EpicGames董事會提名董事[3]。"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-12-30T07:32:39.000Z","msg":"毒撚點會睇財經新聞<br />\n日日淨係睇J圖同有咩新驚出 <img src=